  [False, False,  True,  True]])\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n## Expected Behavior\\\\nThe output should indicate that the inputs and outputs of the linear models are separable and independent, similar to the simpler models.\\\\n\\\\n## Fail-to-pass Tests\\\\n- `astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model6-result6]`\\\\n- `astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model9-result9]`\\\\n\\\\n## Additional Information\\\\nThis seems to be a bug that needs further investigation.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"},{\"id\":\"call_CbgKtpCkHoL7kUu8FQR1yCnQ\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"tests/fail_to_pass/README.md\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"# Fail-to-Pass Test Cases\\\\nThis directory contains details of tests that currently fail, highlighting issues in the code.\\\\n\\\\n## Current Failures\\\\n1. `separability_matrix` fails for nested compound models.\\\\n2. Reference the individual issue files for details.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"}],\"results\":[{\"content\":\"Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-decentralized/tests/fail_to_pass/nested_compound_model_issue.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_decentralized/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_SyyX2PLKiHTBJ79KjGq1POBY\",\"is_error\":false},{\"content\":\"Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-decentralized/tests/fail_to_pass/README.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_decentralized/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_CbgKtpCkHoL7kUu8FQR1yCnQ\",\"is_error\":false}]},\"inner_messages\":[{\"id\":\"ea74d8d3-32ab-4be4-905f-9c9fd3bbecd4\",\"source\":\"ProjectManager\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":2239,\"completion_tokens\":487},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-05T15:59:54.998483Z\"