 the linear models are separable and independent, similar to the simpler models.\\n\\n## Fail-to-pass Tests\\n- `astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model6-result6]`\\n- `astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model9-result9]`\\n\\n## Additional Information\\nThis seems to be a bug that needs further investigation.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_3fpbN4gOBKOSwNMyRJrjcErm", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\": \"fail_to_pass/README.md\", \"content\": \"# Fail-to-Pass Test Cases\\nThis directory contains details of tests that currently fail, highlighting issues in the code.\\n\\n## Current Failures\\n1. `separability_matrix` fails for nested compound models.\\n2. Reference the individual issue files for details.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}]}}], "created": 1777996815, "model": "gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "default", "system_fingerprint": "fp_b6580bbee1", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 483, "prompt_tokens": 4396, "total_tokens": 4879, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4224}}}, "prompt_tokens": 4396, "completion_tokens": 483, "agent_id": "ProjectManager_0f9ea828-36e3-4de5-a69b-f5f78bfa74f7/0f9ea828-36e3-4de5-a69b-f5f78bfa74f7"}
