2026-05-05 23:00:36,460 [INFO] autogen_core: Publishing message of type GroupChatMessage to all subscribers: {'message': ToolCallSummaryMessage(id='d5a92771-c9fe-4343-8e71-e32e3f232060', source='ProjectManager', models_usage=None, metadata={}, created_at=datetime.datetime(2026, 5, 5, 16, 0, 36, 460288, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), content='Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-decentralized/nested_compound_issue.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_decentralized/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board\nAccess denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-decentralized/README.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_decentralized/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board', type='ToolCallSummaryMessage', tool_calls=[FunctionCall(id='call_X8rk75QzhxPjwW1oqWAnFLP1', arguments='{"path": "nested_compound_issue.md", "content": "## Issue Summary\\nModeling\'s `separability_matrix` does not compute separability correctly for nested CompoundModels.\\n\\n## Steps to Reproduce\\n1. Import the necessary modules:\\n    ```python\\n    from astropy.modeling import models as m\\n    from astropy.modeling.separable import separability_matrix\\n    ```\\n2. Create the basic compound model:\\n    ```python\\n    cm = m.Linear1D(10) & m.Linear1D(5)\\n    print(separability_matrix(cm))  # Should output a diagonal matrix.\\n    ```\\n3. Create a more complex model:\\n    ```python\\n    complex_model = m.Pix2Sky_TAN() & cm\\n    print(separability_matrix(complex_model))  # Fails to produce expected separability.\\n    ```\\n\\n## Observed Behavior\\nThe output for the nested compound model incorrectly indicates non-separability:\\n```python\\narray([[ True,  True, False, False],\\n       [ True,  True, False, False],\\n       [False, False,  True,  True],\\n       [False, False,  True,  True]])\\n```\\n\\n## Expected Behavior\\nThe output should indicate that the inputs and outputs of the linear models are separable and independent, similar to the simpler models.\\n\\n## Fail-to-pass Tests\\n- `astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model6-result6]`\\n- `astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model9-result9]`\\n\\n## Additional Information\\nThis seems to be a bug that needs further investigation."}', name='board_write_file'), FunctionCall(id='call_ThLOO7ZIDj88LBJEQKRRQnJC', arguments='{"path": "README.md", "content": "# Nested Compound Model Bug\\nThis document summarizes the issues related to the `separability_matrix` in nested compound models."}', name='board_write_file')], results=[FunctionExecutionResult(content='Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-decentralized/nested_compound_issue.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_decentralized/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board', name='board_write_file', call_id='call_X8rk75QzhxPjwW1oqWAnFLP1', is_error=False), FunctionExecutionResult(content='Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-decentralized/README.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_decentralized/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board', name='board_write_file', call_id='call_ThLOO7ZIDj88LBJEQKRRQnJC', is_error=False)])}
