parability_matrix` and suggest needed changes.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_MFtiRpZDoO3bwObSyon9yjO7", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\": \"implementation/fix_separability_matrix.md\", \"content\": \"## Implementation Task: Fix separability_matrix\\n- **Task**: Update the logic in `separability_matrix` to correctly handle nested CompoundModels.\\n- **Success Criteria**: The function should return the expected diagonal format when dealing with separable inputs and outputs.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_tjRsjZgImFapgDMcnOg9zuzu", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\": \"qa/validation_of_fix.md\", \"content\": \"## QA Validation for Nested Compound Model Fix\\n- **Objective**: Validate the implemented fix for `separability_matrix`. Ensure that tests related to nested CompoundModels pass after the fix.\\n- **Tasks**:\\n  1. Run the modified tests.\\n  2. Document any new issues encountered.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_F6uMzxiP78JLaxq5iRtiVEsr", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\": \"documentation/update_separability_matrix_docs.md\", \"content\": \"## Documentation Update for separability_matrix\\n- **Task**: Update documentation for `separability_matrix` to reflect any changes made during the fix. Include examples of nested CompoundModels.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}]}}], "created": 1777996837, "model": "gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "default", "system_fingerprint": "fp_5652201947", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 696, "prompt_tokens": 5898, "total_tokens": 6594, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 2048}}}, "prompt_tokens": 5898, "completion_tokens": 696, "agent_id": "ProjectManager_0f9ea828-36e3-4de5-a69b-f5f78bfa74f7/0f9ea8